data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the heart of North Phoenix! This exceptional corner unit boasts a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience.

Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood in North Phoenix, this home offers a serene escape while being close to all the amenities the city has to offer. This spacious 2 bed, 2 bath patio home features an intelligently designed floor plan with a focus on functionality and openness.

Enjoy the luxury of extra privacy and abundant natural light and green space with this coveted corner unit.

The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring modern appliances, updated counter space, and stylish cabinetry. Unwind and entertain in your private patio, the ideal spot for morning coffee or evening gatherings with friends and family. Retreat to the generous master suite with an ensuite bathroom and private access to the patio, providing a perfect sanctuary at the end of the day. The additional bedroom is perfect for guests, a home office, or a cozy space for family members. The den can be used as an office space or easily converted to a 3rd bedroom. Abundant storage space throughout the home, including closets and laundry area. Newer Dual Pane windows throughout. One of the few units with a two car garage. Hurry! Won't last long at this price!
